$ at\n$1.15<\\delta<1.3$ (range II) and $T_c=T_2=T_1$ at $1.3<\\delta<1.5$ (range III).\nFor 3NN1 model $T_c=T_2>T_1$ at $0<\\delta<1.2$ (range II) and $T_c=T_2=T_1$ at\n$1.2<\\delta<1.5$ (range III). In range III there is only first order phase\ntransition. In range II the transition at $T_c=T_2$ is of the first order, too.\nIn range I the transition at $T_c$ is either weak first-order or second-order\nphase transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Mar 2014 16:58:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-03"}
