 formation with a\nnon-zero order parameter) is conjectured below a non-zero transition point\n$T_t(q)\\approx0.5$ in the asymptotic regime $q\\to\\infty$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Mar 2014 15:06:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 05:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-09"}
